body:
Thanks @alextp for the help.

Not sure why `fast_tensor_util.cpp` was included in the PR as the filename is actually in `.gitignore`. I have removed the file from PR manually.

The conv1d_transpose has also been imported in `tf.contrib.nn` and exposed. Please take a look.
